---
import DocsPageShell from '../../components/DocsPageShell.astro'
import PromptCard from '../../components/PromptCard.astro'
---

<DocsPageShell
  title="Bundles And Psyche"
  description="An agent bundle is the portable self. The psyche is the part of that self that helps the agent stay oriented to who it is and where it is going."
  eyebrow="Operator Guide"
  canonical="https://ouroboros.bot/docs/bundles-and-psyche"
  intro="This page explains the object. Your agent should inspect the actual bundle to answer file-level questions, because the specific contents are supposed to evolve."
  noteTitle="Recommended handoff"
  noteBody="For deeper help, point your agent at /skills/understand-psyche.md and tell it to inspect the current bundle instead of reciting a canned explanation."
>
  <section class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
    <PromptCard
      prompt={`Inspect the agent bundle I am using right now and explain what lives there. Tell me which files shape your identity, which parts are durable memory, and what looks currently active.`}
      footnote="Best for learning what your current bundle means in practice."
    />
    <PromptCard
      prompt={`Read the psyche files in this bundle and tell me how they work together. Explain the role of each file using the current bundle contents, not generic assumptions.`}
      footnote="Best for understanding the living self-model instead of the abstract file names."
    />
  </section>

  <section class="grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr]">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-canopy bg-undergrowth/30 p-7">
      <p class="font-display text-xl italic text-bone">Evergreen truth</p>
      <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-mist">
        The bundle is the portable boundary of the agent's self. The exact files can evolve,
        but the job stays the same: keep identity, direction, and long-term context somewhere the agent can recover cleanly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-canopy bg-undergrowth/30 p-7">
      <p class="font-display text-xl italic text-bone">What to ask next</p>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-mist">
        <li>Which psyche files matter most for the behavior I want?</li>
        <li>What in this bundle looks stale or contradictory?</li>
        <li>How should my agent update its own direction without losing continuity?</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</DocsPageShell>
